

To compile the GUI code the first time:

  $ sudo aptitude install pyqt4-dev-tools qt4-designer pyqt-tools 
  $ ./compile_gui.sh

To run the GUI:
  $ ./run.sh
or
  $ python spectrometerGUI.py

The swspectrometer program is assumed to be /usr/local/bin/swspectrometer

The included 'sample.ini' is the default template INI file.

To run swspectrometer with plotting you may need to install plplot packages
including the plplot xwin driver.
